snippet.title: Stardust Exile Gameplay January 2023 [Pre-Early Access]
snippet.description:
Updated gameplay video (October 2024): https://youtu.be/C2l6PhGLTkE

Stardust Exile is a RTS set in the Milky Way galaxy, containing currently known stars and exoplanets with their real characteristics. The remaining star systems are procedurally generated based on currently known data. You can create your own ship designs with an in-game ship generator.

Wishlist it on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1858900/Stardust_Exile/
